"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/438698","Home Office","false","2016-01-05","<p>As of 16 December 2015, 3921 Officers have completed the eLearning “Internet and You”. The course forms part of a five stage programme for NCA staff who require detailed training in this area.</p>","South Holland and The Deepings","Mr John Hayes",,"2016-01-05T13:48:35.437Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/438698/answer","Biography information for Sir John Hayes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/438698/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/438698/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2015-12-15","National Crime Agency: Training","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, how many National Crime Agency officers have completed the digital awareness e-learning course, The internet and you.","false","Biography information for Lyn Brown","West Ham","Lyn Brown","20251"
